pageContext.description: width mouth 41.2mm; width blade 34mm; width loop 8.5mm; breadth mouth 44mm; depth socket 90mm; depth int. ribs 59mm,Large bulbous upper moulding above thin belt pronounced lower; rib wing decoration with slight bump between at bottom, or on reverse pellet in similar position; long internal ribs start little below mouth; prob. narrow socket end; remains of casting flash; few odd hammer marks and punch marks on faces; small pit in side prob. casting flaw.
